{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"typedef","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This closure is called when the device registration process finishes, either successfully or with an error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The handler receives two parameters:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"token"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The push token string if registration succeeded, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":" if it failed","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"error"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": An error object if registration failed, or "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if it succeeded"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration result with UI updates and backend sync:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func registerForNotifications() {","    let registrationHandler: PushwooshRegistrationHandler = { token, error in","        if let error = error {","            self.logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","            self.updateNotificationStatus(.failed)","            return","        }","","        guard let token = token else { return }","","        self.logger.info(\"Push token received: \\(token.prefix(20))...\")","        self.updateNotificationStatus(.registered)","","        self.syncPushTokenWithBackend(token)","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(withCompletion: registrationHandler)","}","","func syncPushTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","    let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","    apiClient.post(\"\/devices\/register\", body: [","        \"push_token\": token,","        \"hwid\": hwid,","        \"platform\": \"ios\"","    ])","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler"]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}],"externalID":"c:PWTypes.h@T@PushwooshRegistrationHandler","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"symbolKind":"typealias","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","roleHeading":"Type Alias"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler"],"title":"Related Documentation"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Push notification SDK for iOS applications.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshFramework","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshRegistrationHandler":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler","title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshErrorHandler":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler","fragments":[{"text":"typealias","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshErrorHandler"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshErrorHandler","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when an operation fails.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwoosherrorhandler","role":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/title","op":"replace","value":"PushwooshErrorHandler"},{"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/fragments","op":"replace","value":[{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}]}]}]}